{"tid":1421063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"毛澤東語錄: 敵進我退，敵駐我擾，敵疲我打，敵退我追","createTime":"2019-08-06T06:47:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T07:37:42.000Z","uid":57076,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"43396c03ba26622e9ff77f3eeede7979d128331a","tid":1421063,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:47:20.000Z","msg":"眾所週知，毛澤東一嚮主張&ldquo;人民戰爭&rdquo;，甚至主張&ldquo;全民皆兵&rdquo;，這種軍事思想，在井冈山時期就已形成。<br />\n毛澤東有篇大作《井冈山的鬥爭》，他寫道：&ldquo;邊界的鬥爭，完全是軍事的鬥爭，黨和群眾不得不一齊軍事化。怎樣對付敵人，怎樣作戰，成了日常生活的中心問題。所謂割據，必須是武裝的。那一處沒有武裝，或者武裝不夠，或者對付敵人的策略錯了，地方就立即被敵人佔去了。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">毛澤東:<br />\n敵進我退，敵駐我擾，敵疲我打，敵退我追<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">敵進我退</span></span><br />\n如果敵人兵力太多，或者無路可走(例如無地鐵)，並且三面圍城就要退<br />\n<br />\nBe water極致就係快閃游擊，但必須小心深藍地區，例如北角(被稱為小福建)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">敵駐我擾</span></span><br />\n敵人一嚟就<br />\n1.街坊屌敵人<br />\n2.laser兵出動<br />\n3.玩雞蛋<br />\n4.玩波子<br />\n5.油漆<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">敵疲我打</span></span><br />\n敵人一想休息<br />\n落部分裝備坐係度<br />\n遠攻手們出動了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">敵退我進</span></span><br />\n如果敵人開始想撤退，呢個時候就要勇武，草木皆兵<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有一個:<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">敵強我散<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n敵人太多，而且敵人熟晒路<br />\n就要be water，轉場"},{"pid":"129927a7f2b3b513a1d5f5b4d446c95f04148823","tid":1421063,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:57:29.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"a67bec8f789d206245be203d7b18fc6decb27984","tid":1421063,"uid":295518,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:00:02.000Z","msg":"光復香港後係咪照跟行共產？"},{"pid":"1ce086cfed6996c80138455ef6c1dfb29b11cb39","tid":1421063,"uid":263464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:00:08.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命 要傳比大眾嘅訊息可能係<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1420975\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1420975</a>"},{"pid":"6bfc3f0749119feab351a205d874c16fc3d13d26","tid":1421063,"uid":57076,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a67bec8f789d206245be203d7b18fc6decb27984","tid":1421063,"uid":295518,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:00:02.000Z","msg":"光復香港後係咪照跟行共產？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:02:25.000Z","msg":"p牌仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n毛澤東革命思想同建國後唔同<br />\n只可以話<br />\nPower&nbsp;tends tocorrupt, and&nbsp;absolute power corrupts absolutely"},{"pid":"f5f7a4287928dfa1fecf8d1c659cadec5f1f25a0","tid":1421063,"uid":295518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:46:03.000Z","msg":"革命未成功要人信佢；要人同佢企埋一齊就緊係講得好聽啦，有幾多個唔會戀權丫，"},{"pid":"12c785b59a2a17c3a913180ecb6106271fa966ce","tid":1421063,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5f7a4287928dfa1fecf8d1c659cadec5f1f25a0","tid":1421063,"uid":295518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:46:03.000Z","msg":"革命未成功要人信佢；要人同佢企埋一齊就緊係講得好聽啦，有幾多個唔會戀權丫，"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:18:50.000Z","msg":"天琦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0871603ecf3a383d85cfe186d071dc7780c8537f","tid":1421063,"uid":295518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:31:15.000Z","msg":"就算香港獨立後，只會又捲入另一場鬥爭"},{"pid":"ea0d4423deea07ef2994c48a21a8ab8e198b8d39","tid":1421063,"uid":157597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:33:58.000Z","msg":"推，真係要咁"},{"pid":"876e247fa928934b2c41c406334c1953c1465a7d","tid":1421063,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,