><span style=\"color: gold;\">［抗分化］共匪宜家玩緊老技倆，群眾鬥群眾，拉一派打一派</span></span><br />\n<br />\n共匪一貫手法，分化、滲透，然後拉籠一派打一派，政府有時會軟硬兼施，打下感情牌博同情，亦會派三毛做打手，屌/笑/鬧/玩膠嗰啲當然90%都係三毛，但亦都唔排除有真心膠中計信咗佢地一套，所謂拉一派打一派，群眾鬥群眾就係咁，要你自相殘殺，孤立主要敵人，然後共匪就可以輕鬆逐個擊破，普羅大眾應該要明白呢一點，<span style=\"color: red;\">2014年雨革因示威者內部分裂而亡，切記歷史教訓，和理非同埋勇武必須同心合作，互相掩護</span>，無論如何都唔可以比三毛成功分化<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請廣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T23:30:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e0b78cb9eb446e583ccaa1af142529d94c10bc7","tid":1421063,"uid":133525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a67bec8f789d206245be203d7b18fc6decb27984","tid":1421063,"uid":295518,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:00:02.000Z","msg":"光復香港後係咪照跟行共產？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T23:37:13.000Z","msg":"毛澤東主義萬歲"},{"pid":"0130b5be5ea0c1e388e708db1352af6b31649416","tid":1421063,"uid":168675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T23:50:43.000Z","msg":"岩 Be water 不被捕 不受傷"},{"pid":"8377bddb44c4050d6fef5da314cf38cd1165324e","tid":1421063,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"113a711442c337074ee09f2877d7fe49a23f795a","tid":1421063,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb4b1e08efbac795eb1a0bbd2f73fc5daef3a3e1","tid":1421063,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T22:49:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1woYGqS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1woYGqS.jpg&h=bdc24474&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T23:24:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:58:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gdhyv2n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgdhyv2n.jpg&h=e724f87b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nupload錯咗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2577a9b0436a206486981afd4521197c96d5315","tid":1421063,"uid":31151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:00:24.000Z","msg":"敵退我進 示範:早兩日黃大仙磚頭雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27aab50e06ea67df8d8cc6d7e57c0b0da37dce42","tid":1421063,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0871603ecf3a383d85cfe186d071dc7780c8537f","tid":1421063,"uid":295518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:31:15.000Z","msg":"就算香港獨立後，只會又捲入另一場鬥爭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:21:56.000Z","msg":"點解會有呢個必然性既推論？<br />\n你想講乜？想我地坐係到咩都唔做？"},{"pid":"fb01458b87597ff86ff41d6c776aa69097ad61c7","tid":1421063,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2577a9b0436a206486981afd4521197c96d5315","tid":1421063,"uid":31151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:00:24.000Z","msg":"敵退我進 示範:早兩日黃大仙磚頭雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:40:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"141049bc3a47178969de28324d8850ba0edf3004","tid":1421063,"uid":295518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27aab50e06ea67df8d8cc6d7e57c0b0da37dce42","tid":1421063,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0871603ecf3a383d85cfe186d071dc7780c8537f","tid":1421063,"uid":295518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:31:15.000Z","msg":"就算香港獨立後，只會又捲入另一場鬥爭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:21:56.000Z","msg":"點解會有呢個必然性既推論？<br />\n你想講乜？想我地坐係到咩都唔做？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:56:45.000Z","msg":"呢個推論係跟據人類發展歷史所得，基本上有人嘅地方就有鬥爭，簡單啲講就係到時邊個做領導邊個揸數你估又唔會爭？<br />\n<br />\n宜家唔係乜都唔做，但塞住架地鐵唔比人返工，放火，封路，打人，係咪會快啲成功？<br />\n要做就要對準目標，要搵就搵最大嗰個，直接去禮賓府圍林鄭，圍警務署長，圍解放軍，咁先有用，正所謂擒賊先擒王，下面啲人點做都係佢意思，咁樣唔係最有效率咩，特別係解放軍，香港駐軍係對呢個地方有主權嘅象徵，要解除呢種象徵意義，就要同佢對抗，但點解圍嚟圍去都唔去軍營？塞住紅隧塞住屯門公路係冇用"},{"pid":"ddb3324c9b9d3a8b20593cdd3927037fb1deed5c","tid":1421063,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:37:42.000Z","msg":"p牌三毛嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}